Ep 12: Off the Bench
Kim throws Kroy a surprise party before he heads off to training camp.

The new and improved Kim throws Kroy a surprise party with his closest friends from near and far before he heads off to training camp. Having been out of commission for almost the entire season with a torn Achilles, the moment of truth has arrived for Kroy to say goodbye to his family and return to football.
